spec_data.Name: python3-backports-unittest_mock
spec_data.Description:
Provides a function “install()” which makes the “mock” module
available as “unittest.mock” on Python 3.2 and earlier.

Also advertises a pytest plugin which configures
unittest.mock automatically.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:54:37 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: backport of unittest mock for python 3.2 and before
